	librib2stream/.cvsignore, libslparse/.cvsignore, render/.cvsignore,
	ribfiles/.cvsignore, shaders/.cvsignore, shadowmap/.cvsignore,
	slpp/.cvsignore, teqser/.cvsignore: Various updates to clean up CVS
	ignoring.

